Rating: 3
I tried a couple of crab cake recipes over thanksgiving. I ended up using this recipe but added a 1/4 cup capers and a 1/4 cup diced red pepper and a tablespoon of corse mustard instead of the dry mustard. Adding the ingredients gave the recipe the flavor and color that the original was missing.

