Rating: 4
I've made it twice. Just get the best crabmeat you can. Second time wasn't as good because I couldn't find the better crabmeat. As the recipe suggests the simple ingredients allow the flavor to come through. Great for entertaining, made 12 crab cakes for 6 people out of recipe and added about 1/4 cup of minced red pepper and 1/4 cup of corn kernels to add color. Served with a mesclun salad with simple vinagrette on the same plate and only spent 5 minutes away from my guests.

